description.en: ShipItPro is a fast-growing cross-border eCommerce software company headquartered in Tallinn, Estonia. The company is currently focused on building the world’s first full-scale eCommerce services platform and application enabling sellers and importers from the EU and 3rd countries to sell to the EU with a fast, transparent and seamless process that is secured with blockchain-based timestamp. The full-scale solution will provide the cross-border eCommerce companies all of the necessary components of cross-border online trade: CO2 tax management, green delivery, VAT & import duty management, payments, insurance and returns handling.
